import React, { Component } from 'react' import {Grid, Image} from 'semantic-ui-react' export default class ESocial extends Component { DESCRIPTION = 'Every Friday at 4:30 pm ESG invites a company or campus organization to host an E-Social at Twinnie’s, located in Fitzpatrick – Ciemas. We provide free beer (for upperclassmen) and free food (for everyone). This event is a great way to network with companies and other engineers!' IMAGE_PATH = './images/' render(){ return(
{this.DESCRIPTION}
) } } {/* Where? Twinnie's Cafe (in E-Quad)! */}
